high_descs: Turn to the left and move around the island to locate the sink.
Pick up the cup from the sink.
Carry the cup and turn around and find the fridge on the left.
Open the fridge and place the cup inside. Shut the door then open it. Take out the cup and shut the door.
Hold the cup and turn around, then right to face the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the cup inside, shut the door.
walk forwards to the kitchen sink at the end of the room
grab the white cup out of the kitchen sink
turn around and walk over to the fridge on the left
place the cup inside of the fridge, let it cool, then take it back out
move to the left a bit to face the microwave better
place the cup inside of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a cooled cup inside of the microwave

high_descs: Walk forward and left to the sink, swinging left and right as you do so.
Pick up the mug from the sink.
Turn right, walk to refrigerator, turn left to face refrigerator.
Open refrigerator, put mug in it, close door, wait a bit, open the door, take mug out of fridge.
Go to the microwave on counter directly to left of fridge and face it.
Put the mug in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled coffee mug in the microwave.
